high_descs: Go toward the fridge, turn right and move forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Pick up the butter knife in the sink.
Turn left and go to the wall, then turn left and look up to the cabinet.
Open the cabinet and put the butter knife in the rightmost cup.
Take the rightmost cup from the cabinet.
Turn left and move forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Put the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a butter knife in it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn and walk to the sink on the right.
Pick up the butter knife from the sink.
Turn left, turn left at the window, and face the counter with the coffee maker on it, look above the counter at the cabinet.
Open both cabinet doors. put the knife down in the glass on the right.
Pick up the glass from the cabinet and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the glass inside of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To put a knife in the glass and put the glass in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and move to stand in front of the sink.
Pick up the butter knife from inside the sink.
Turn left and move to stand in front of the coffee maker right after the stove.
Open the cupboard above the coffee maker and place the knife in the green cup on the right..
Pick up the cup with the knife inside from the cupboard.
Turn left and carry the cup and knife to the sink.
Place the cup with the knife inside in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a knife in a cup to the sink.
